1
00:00:08,797 --> 00:00:12,917
That's Thursday, November 17th, at the hotel.
那是星期四, 11月17日, 在酒店.

2
00:00:12,918 --> 00:00:14,145
All day?
一整天?

3
00:00:14,146 --> 00:00:16,762
Yes. We start at 8:30 in the morning.
是的. 咱们开始于8:30  在早上

4
00:00:17,301 --> 00:00:18,571
With coffee.
与咖啡(一起).

5
00:00:18,572 --> 00:00:21,800
Yes. Coffee starts at 8:30 and ends at 9.
是的. 咖啡开始于8:30, 结束于9点.

6
00:00:21,801 --> 00:00:24,988
... eight-thirty to nine.
... 8点半到9点.

7
00:00:24,989 --> 00:00:28,180
The opening address begins at 9 o'clock sharp.
开幕辞开始于9点 整.

8
00:00:28,180 --> 00:00:28,208
Workshops run from 9：30 to noon.
研讨会从9:30到正午.

10
00:00:30,600 --> 00:00:31,740
Then lunch.
然后午餐.

11
00:00:31,742 --> 00:00:32,956
One hour?
1小时?

12
00:00:32,957 --> 00:00:33,940
Yes.
对的

13
00:00:33,941 --> 00:00:38,053
The second session goes from one to about 4:15.
第二场从1点到大约4:15.

14
00:00:38,120 --> 00:00:40,180
Discussion ends at 4:45.
讨论结束于4:45.

15
00:00:40,260 --> 00:00:42,020
Then a small reception.
然后一个小招待会.

16
00:00:42,118 --> 00:00:43,772
Until what time?
直到什么时间?

17
00:00:43,895 --> 00:00:46,949
Oh...  Sorry.
Oh... 对不起

18
00:00:47,240 --> 00:00:49,508
That's my watch alarm.
那是我的手表闹钟.

19
00:00:49,612 --> 00:00:52,735
I have an appointment back at the hotel at eleven o'clock.
我有个预约 在酒店 在11点钟时

20
00:00:52,778 --> 00:00:54,429
Is it eleven already?
11点了  已经?

21
00:00:54,430 --> 00:00:57,063
No, no. Actually, it's 10:30.
没, 没. 事实呢, 是10:30.

22
00:00:57,064 --> 00:00:59,418
I set my watch half an hour fast.
我把我的表调快了半个小时.

23
00:00:59,419 --> 00:01:00,728
You're never late, are you?
你永远不迟到, 是吗?

24
00:01:00,729 --> 00:01:02,575
Never. I can't be!
永不. 我不能(迟到)!

